<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="luckily-adv">luckily <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'lʌkɪli/    美 /'lʌkɪli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-fortunately">1.★ <strong>幸运地；幸好 (fortunately)</strong></h4>
<p>反 unluckily </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Luckily nobody was killed in that incident. 
幸运的是，没有人在那次事件中丧生。</p></div></div>